message: As far as everyone knows, there is NO HD CHANNEL, and it is NOT IN THE PIPELINE! If you want to discuss the HD channel, please use the talk page and provide a source.

Season 3 - present is filmed in full HD, and is not edited at all. It depends on the region and broadcaster. For example - Disney Channel USA chooses to broadcast in 720p, whereas Brazil prefers 1080i
